OL,4,CChurch shortlists for senior posts
OL,5,C'must include ethnic minorities'
OL,6, All shortlists for senior Church of
OL,7, England posts must include at least one
OL,8, ethnic minority candidate, a report has
OL,9, said.
OL,11,FIt is one of 47 recommendations made by
OL,12,Fthe Archbishops' Anti-Racism Taskforce,
OL,13,Fwhich was established last year after
OL,14,Fthe Black Lives Matter protests.
OL,16,FIt said the Church has "an alarmingly
OL,17,Fretrograde trend" when it comes to
OL,18,Fethnic minority senior bishops.
OL,20,FFailing to act would have "devastating
OL,21,Feffects" on the future of the Church.
